#Tesla Sales vs. Oil Prices

msg.data: Tesla Sales vs. Oil Prices

paragraphs.title: Global Oil Price From 2013 - 2016
paragraphs.text:
select Entry_Date, Europe_Price 
from Global_Oil_Prices 
where Entry_Date > DATE '2012-12-31' 
order by Entry_Date asc;
